Unique subjects within a data set

Source: R/nif_class.R
subjects.Rd

Unique subjects within a data set

Usage

subjects(obj)

Arguments

obj

The data set, either a nif or a sdtm object.

Value

A data frame.

Examples

subjects(examplinib_fe_nif)
